# Architecture Diagrams for RHOAI 2.14 Components

Generated from: `architecture/rhoai-2.14/*.md`
Date: 2026-03-15

**Note**: Diagram filenames use base component name without version (directory is already versioned).

## Components

This directory contains architecture diagrams for the following RHOAI 2.14 components:

1. **[CodeFlare Operator](#codeflare-operator)** - Distributed ML training and batch scheduling
2. **[Data Science Pipelines Operator](#data-science-pipelines-operator)** - ML workflow orchestration (Kubeflow Pipelines)
3. **[KServe](#kserve)** - Model serving platform
4. **[Kubeflow (ODH Notebook Controller)](#kubeflow-odh-notebook-controller)** - Jupyter notebook management
5. **[KubeRay](#kuberay)** - Ray cluster management for distributed computing
6. **[ModelMesh Serving](#modelmesh-serving)** - Model serving management and routing layer
7. **[Model Registry Operator](#model-registry-operator)** - ML model registry deployment and management
8. **[Notebooks](#notebooks)** - Pre-built workbench container images (Jupyter, code-server, RStudio)
9. **[ODH Model Controller](#odh-model-controller)** - KServe InferenceService extension with OpenShift integration, service mesh, and authorization

